data.description: DON'T WAIT TO BUILD! Built in 2018 by DR Horton in the gated community of The Villages of Glen Creek. A master planned community featuring a resort style pool, clubhouse, play area and sidewalks. Situated on a corner lot. This one-story home includes many contemporary features, and an open-concept design and 8’8" ceilings enhance the wonderful feel of this home. The kitchen includes a large island perfect for bar-style eating or entertaining, a pantry, and plenty of cabinets and counter space. The well-appointed kitchen comes with all appliances including a refrigerator, built-in dishwasher, electric range, and microwave hood. The dining room and living room both overlook the covered lanai, which is a great area for relaxing and dining. The large owner’s suite, located at the back of the home for privacy, can comfortably fit a king-size bed and includes an en-suite bathroom with double vanity, a walk-in closet, and a separate linen closet. At the front of the home, two spacious bedrooms share a second bathroom. The two-car garage connects to the front hallway where the laundry room, equipped with included washer and dryer, and an extra storage closet is also located. Step outside to the backyard, where you'll find a screened in patio area overlooking a meticulously maintained lawn that is fenced in by a white PVC 6" foot fence for complete privacy – an ideal spot for outdoor gatherings or a quiet evening under the stars. Ultra-fi Community a unique internet and cable TV bundled $75 HOA each month(includes internet, cable tv and community pool and club house within walking distance) experience for the perfect work from home. Perfect for an investment with rental opportunity as well.Schedule a viewing today and experience the perfect blend of style, comfort, and convenient location close to everything including beaches, Sarasota airport, UTC mall and all conveniences you need. Perfect for an investment with rental opportunity as well.
